OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FFine and dry
OL,6,Finto the evening but thickening cloud
OL,7,Fand strengthening winds overnight will
OL,8,Fbring patchy outbreaks of rain to all
OL,9,Fareas by the early hours.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FEarly outbreaks of rain
OL,12,Fclearing slowly into the afternoon
OL,13,Fwith winds easing somewhat. Brighter
OL,14,Fto end the day although isolated
OL,15,Fshowers are expected and conditions
OL,16,Fremaining breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
